<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَن تُؤْمِنُوا}</span> ... لِأَجْلِ إِيمَانِكُمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضَلَّ سَوَاءَ السَّبِيلِ}</span> ... أَخْطَأَ طَرِيقَ الهُدَى.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَثْقَفُوكُمْ}</span> ... يَظْفَرُوا بِكُمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيَبْسُطُوا}</span> ... يَمُدُّوا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَفْصِلُ بَيْنَكُمْ}</span> ... يُفَرِّقُ بَيْنَ المُطِيعِينَ، وَالعَاصِينَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
