<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُرَءَاؤُا}</span> ... بَرِيئُونَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِلَّا قَوْلَ إِبْرَاهِيمَ}</span> ... لَكِنْ لَا تَقْتَدُوا بِإِبْرَاهِيمَ حِينَ قَالَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَنَبْنَا}</span> ... رَجَعْنَا بِالتَّوْبَةِ، وَالطَّاعَةِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
